207
00:12:39,540 --> 00:12:40,490
Oh, no...

208
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:46,410
Listen, you guys. Pirates are scum.

209
00:12:43,450 --> 00:12:46,410
"Navy Headquarters Sergeant,
Jango the Traitor"

210
