Hey, what're you saying?
Don't you remember?

211
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:52,410
"Navy Headquarters Sergeant,
Iron Fists Fullbody"

212
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:52,410
You used to be a pirate, right?

213
00:12:52,410 --> 00:12:57,020
Urk! That's right! You're exactly right, baby!

214
00:12:57,020 --> 00:12:58,240
Wanna dance?!

215
00:12:58,240 --> 00:13:00,710
Ahh! Yeah! Dance! Dance!

216
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,400
Dance! Dance!

217
00:13:06,110 --> 00:13:08,570
Looks like those two took down
the enemy ship and returned.

218
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:12,570
It took them forever.
I wonder what they were doing.

219
00:13:12,570 --> 00:13:16,720
I put trust in their ability and left the
ship we were attacking in their hands...

220
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:19,060
Disappointed. I'm disappointed.

221
00:13:19,510 --> 00:13:21,150
