229
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:38,750
Don't tell me they've
already left this country...

230
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:40,510
No... I don't think that's the case...

231
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:43,080
Then search for it... every corner of the coast!

232
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,460
Yes, ma'am! Will do!

233
00:13:44,460 --> 00:13:47,840
--Geez...
--Miss Hina! Sorry it took so long!

234
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:50,330
