236
00:13:52,090 --> 00:13:55,020
--We were picking flowers... for you...!
--Don't need them.

237
00:13:55,420 --> 00:13:58,910
Man your positions right away!
We'll take down the Straw Hat gang!

238
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:00,480
